            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De causidicis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
      ¶ De causidicis et causidictione. Rubrica. 10
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e115">TUllius de oratore lib. 2.</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e125">Ego sepissime vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>deo in causis aliquid male facere:
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>homines minime malos.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e131">Ouidius epistolarum. 19 e. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e137">Optima non
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>vllo causa tuente perit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e144"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e142">Idem de arte amandi
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>li. 3. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e146">Ius qui prositebitur assit
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>Facundus causam sepe clientis agat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e157">Idem de ponto li. 2. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e158">Non est con
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>fessi causa tuenti rei.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e169">Quintilianus dclamationum 10 declam.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e168">Multum me vel vos fallit opinio iudices: si
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>vllam causam ita euidentem deferri in forum
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>posse putatis: cui nulla ne mendacii quidem
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>velamenta contingant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e186">Iuuenalis lib. 3 satura i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e184">Purpuram vendit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Causidicum vendi tunc ametistina conueni illis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>Est strepitum: a facie maioris viuere census.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e192">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e200">Lex diges. ti. de ori. iur. l. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e196">In foro causas
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>dicentibus nefas: vt ita dixerim videtur esse
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>nulla praefatione facta iudici rem exponere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e214">Lex codi. ti. de postulando. l. quisquis.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e208">Siquis adeo procax fuerit vt non ratione sed
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>probris putet esse certandum. Opinionis sue <!--142.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="58-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>munitionem patietur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e226"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e234">Ti. de aduoca. di
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>uer. iudi. l. laudabile:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e228">Laudabile viteque ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>minum necessarium aduocationis officium: pre
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>miis oportet remunerari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e238"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e249">Tit. si per vim
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>vel alio modo etcaetera. l. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e240">Negociorum merita
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>partium assertione panduntur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-d1e248">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Rd1e264">Prouerb. exor. l. vagam.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d43736-Qd1e252">In propria causa
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>aduocatum quere.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
